OL,3,CWoman killed loving husband and text
OL,4,Cmum saying 'I've done something awful'
OL,6,FA woman who fatally stabbed her
OL,7,Fhusband at their Somerset home has
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of his murder.
OL,10,FHenri Kekkonen died on 9 May at the
OL,11,Fcouple's home in Dunford Terrace,
OL,12,FBaltonsborough.
OL,14,FHis wife, Christine Kekkonen, stabbed
OL,15,Fher husband in the neck. The 36-year-
OL,16,Fold claimed she did not intend to
OL,17,Finjure him, but a jury at Bristol
OL,18,FCrown Court found her guilty of murder
OL,19,Fon on Friday 29 November following a
OL,20,Ftrial.
