OL,3,CWoman killed loving husband and text
OL,4,Cmum saying 'I've done something awful'
OL,6,FThe jury heard Mr Kekkonen was
OL,7,Fattacked at some point between 4pm and
OL,8,F4.20pm that day.
OL,10,FAt 4.21pm Mrs Kekkonen sent a text
OL,11,Fmessage to her mum saying: "Mum,
OL,12,Fplease get the police here now.
OL,13,FPlease. I've done something awful."
OL,15,FHer dad then called for an ambulance,
OL,16,Fand police were informed.
OL,18,FWithin 15 minutes, emergency services
OL,19,Fwere at the couple's home. Henri died
OL,20,Fat the scene.
