OL,6,FA search of the house led to the
OL,7,Fdiscovery of a knife. Mrs Kekkonen was
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,9,Flater charged.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Lorett
OL,12,FSpierenburg, the senior investigating
OL,13,Fofficer, said: "Henri was a loving
OL,14,Fhusband who aged 41 had so much more
OL,15,Flife to live. Those opportunities were
OL,16,Fcruelly taken from him.
OL,18,F"Christine Kekkonen is clearly a
OL,19,Fvulnerable woman, but her actions that
OL,20,Fafternoon have cut short the life of a
OL,21,Fman who completely doted on her.
