OL,6,F"I am pleased for Henri's family that
OL,7,Fthe woman responsible for his death
OL,8,Fhas today been convicted of his murder
OL,9,Fand my thoughts remain with them."
OL,11,FMrs Kekkonen will be sentenced on
OL,12,FFriday 28 March next year.
